    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;In order for IP multicast traffic within a BGP/MPLS IP VPN (Virtual Private Network) to travel from one VPN site to another, special protocols and procedures must be implemented by the VPN Service Provider.  These protocols and procedures are specified in this document. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
